---
const effectiveDate = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' });
---
<div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-gutter py-section" id="privacy-policy">
  <div class="bg-surface-container-low/50 border border-border-glass rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-14 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Decorative glow -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-125 h-125 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3 pointer-events-none"></div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-6 mb-12 pb-8 border-b border-border-glass relative z-10">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-5">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary-container/20 flex items-center justify-center border border-primary/20 shadow-inner">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">privacy_tip</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface tracking-tight mb-1">Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Your privacy is our absolute priority.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface/50 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-border-glass text-sm text-primary/80 self-start md:self-auto font-medium">
        Effective Date: {effectiveDate}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-12 relative z-10">
      
      <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
        Welcome to JobForm Copilot ("we," "our," or "us"). This policy explains how we keep your information completely safe and strictly on your device. We intentionally have no servers, meaning we do not collect, store, or transmit your personal data.
      </p>

      <!-- Section 1 -->
      <div class="bg-surface/30 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border-glass hover:bg-surface/50 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="flex items-center gap-3 font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-6">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold border border-border-glass text-primary shadow-sm">1</span>
          Information We (Don't) Collect
        </h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          JobForm Copilot is engineered from the ground up to operate <strong>100% locally</strong> on your device.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary/70 text-2xl mt-1">key</span>
            <div>
              <strong class="block text-on-surface mb-1">API Keys</strong>
              <span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Securely encrypted and stored entirely within your browser's local storage. They are never sent to us.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary/70 text-2xl mt-1">description</span>
            <div>
              <strong class="block text-on-surface mb-1">PDF Resumes</strong>
              <span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Documents are processed locally. Text is sent directly to your AI provider. We cannot see or log these files.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 md:col-span-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary/70 text-2xl mt-1">input</span>
            <div>
              <strong class="block text-on-surface mb-1">Form Data</strong>
              <span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Autofill actions happen strictly on the client-side. We do not track the websites you visit or the information you fill in.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 2 -->
      <div class="bg-surface/30 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border-glass hover:bg-surface/50 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="flex items-center gap-3 font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-4">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold border border-border-glass text-primary shadow-sm">2</span>
          Third-Party Services
        </h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          Our extension acts as a secure bridge between your browser and your chosen AI provider (e.g., OpenAI or Anthropic). When you process a resume, the data is sent directly to that provider. We strongly recommend reviewing the privacy policies of the AI provider you choose to use.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 3 & 4 (Grid) -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-surface/30 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border-glass hover:bg-surface/50 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="flex items-center gap-3 font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-4">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold border border-border-glass text-primary shadow-sm">3</span>
            Data Security
          </h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
            By eliminating centralized servers, we eliminate the risk of a central data breach. Your data's security relies entirely on your device's security and your browser's built-in encryption mechanisms.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-surface/30 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border-glass hover:bg-surface/50 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="flex items-center gap-3 font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-4">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold border border-border-glass text-primary shadow-sm">4</span>
            Contact Us
          </h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Have questions about our privacy practices? We'd love to hear from you.
          </p>
          <a href="https://tally.so/r/Bz9QR1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary hover:text-primary-fixed transition-colors font-medium bg-primary/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">mail</span>
            Send us a message
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
